      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "This answer previously suggested using <code>transient</code> (as in <code>private transient String password;</code>) but <a href=\"https://github.com/FasterXML/jackson-databind/issues/296\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">transient fields with public getters are ignored</a> unless <a href=\"https://fasterxml.github.io/jackson-databind/javadoc/2.8/com/fasterxml/jackson/databind/MapperFeature.html#PROPAGATE_TRANSIENT_MARKER\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">MapperFeature.PROPAGATE_TRANSIENT_MARKER</a> is enabled."
