      "comment_id" : 29089250,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "That works if your attribute is really transient, not ORM involved, for example....Found @JsonIgnore to be more interesting in my case, though I would be locked to jackson, but it&#39;s a good tradeoff"
    }, {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 365547,
