    "answer_id" : 40801363,
    "question_id" : 9112900,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>One should ask why you would want a public getter method for the password. Hibernate, or any other ORM framework, will do with a private getter method. For checking whether the password is correct, you can use</p>\n\n<pre><code>public boolean checkPassword(String password){\n  return this.password.equals(anyHashingMethod(password));\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
